prediction.sparql:
PREFIX rdfs: <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#>
PREFIX wdt: <http://www.wikidata.org/prop/direct/>
PREFIX wd: <http://www.wikidata.org/entity/>
SELECT ?item WHERE {
  ?item rdfs:label "the last Egyptian" @en .
  ?item wdt:P31 wd:Q5
}

PREFIX wd: <http://www.wikidata.org/entity/>
PREFIX wdt: <http://www.wikidata.org/prop/direct/>
SELECT ?work ?title WHERE {
  ?work wdt:P136 wd:Q1080374 .
  ?work wdt:P31 wd:Q7725634 .
  ?work wdt:P1476 ?title .
  FILTER ( LANG( ?title ) = 'en' )
}
LIMIT 1

PREFIX wd: <http://www.wikidata.org/entity/>
PREFIX wdt: <http://www.wikidata.org/prop/direct/>
SELECT ( AVG( ?semi_major_axis ) AS ?avg_semi_major_axis ) ( AVG( ?eccentricity ) AS ?avg_eccentricity ) ( AVG( ?inclination ) AS ?avg_inclination ) ( AVG( ?period ) AS ?avg_period ) ?parent_body WHERE {
  wd:Q2627790 wdt:P2233 ?semi_major_axis .
  wd:Q2627790 wdt:P1096 ?eccentricity .
  wd:Q2627790 wdt:P2045 ?inclination .
  wd:Q2627790 wdt:P2146 ?period .
  wd:Q2627790 wdt:P397 ?parent_body .
}
GROUP BY ?parent_body
